<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Black & White Document Hub</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles - Strict Black and White */
        body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000000;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Scrolling Text Banner */
        .scroll-container {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            overflow: hidden;
            white-space: nowrap;
            padding: 10px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .scroll-text {
            display: inline-block;
            animation: scroll-left 15s linear infinite;
            padding-left: 100%;
        }

        @keyframes scroll-left {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
            100% { transform: translate(-100%, 0); }
        }

        /* Navigation Menu */
        nav {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 1px solid #000000;
            padding: 5px 10px;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* Main Content Area */
        main {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .document-section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #000000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="scroll-container">
        <div class="scroll-text">
            WELCOME TO THE DOCUMENT HUB // LATEST UPDATES LOADED // SCROLLING TEXT TYPE SYSTEM // 
        </div>
    </div>

    <header>
        <h1>Archive System</h1>
        
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#doc1">Document 01</a></li>
                <li><a href="#doc2">Document 02</a></li>
                <li><a href="#doc3">Document 03</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="doc1" class="document-section">
            <h2>Document 01: Overview</h2>
            <p>This is the first document section. Clicking "Document 01" in the menu will jump directly here. The design uses strict black and white tones with a monospace font for a clean, retro look.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="doc2" class="document-section">
            <h2>Document 02: Specifications</h2>
            <p>This is the second document section. You can fill this area with your text, reports, or data logs. Everything is styled to scale nicely on both computers and mobile screens.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="doc3" class="document-section">
            <h2>Document 03: Notes</h2>
            <p>This is the third document section. You can easily add more sections by copying this structure and updating the ID tags to match your menu links.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
